name: CHARGED ⚡️ 2021
description: I am finally in remission from chronic migraine (the 6th most disabling illness and one of the most painful in the world). I can draw again! Very slowly and patiently because I still have the damned illness.. But it's happening! This is a thank you piece dedicated to everyone that supported me my online healing journey and to anyone that wants to wish me good luck for my re entry in the art world.
